section_text: There are 16 Commonwealth realms currently with a combined area ( excluding Antarctic claims ) of 18.7 million km2 ( 7.2 million mi2 ) [ 1 ] and a population of around 148 million , [ 2 ] of which all but about two million live in the six most populous : the United Kingdom , Canada , Australia , Papua New Guinea , New Zealand , and Jamaica
